39;<br />Advanced: &#10004;&#65039;<br />&nbsp;<br /><u>What are the key technique points?<br /></u><ul><li>Keep your elbow directly under your shoulder as you are setting up to side plank</li><li>Squeeze your abs and glutes, lining up your body from front to back (like a standard plank) before lifting up into the side plank position.</li><li>Maintain alignment through the shoulders, hips, knees and ankles by bracing your core to keep tight.</li><li>Start on your weaker side if you struggle and remember to swap side to work the full body.</li></ul></div>  <div class="wsite-youtube" style="margin-bottom:10px;margin-top:10px;"><div class="wsite-youtube-wrapper wsite-youtube-size-auto wsite-youtube-align-center"> <div class="wsite-youtube-container">  <iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/DrxqMVN-b9k?wmode=opaque" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe> </div> </div></div>  <div class="paragraph"><span style="color:rgb(42, 42, 42)">If you'd like to have everything taken care of for you then I offer both in-person&nbsp;<a href="https://www.strengthcoachglasgow.co.uk/personal-training.html">1-2-1 personal training in Glasgow</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="https://www.strengthcoachglasgow.co.uk/online-training.html">online personal training</a>. You can check them out by clicking each option or&nbsp;<a href="https://www.strengthcoachglasgow.co.uk/contact.html">send me a message now</a>&nbsp;if you have any questions.</span><br /><br /><span style="color:rgb(42, 42, 42)">Follow me on Instagram to keep up with the latest events, news and tips.&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.instagram.com/StrengthCoachGlasgow/" target="_blank">@StrengthCoachGlasgow</a></div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Exercise Spotlight – Snatch]]></title><link><![CDATA[https://www.strengthcoachglasgow.co.uk/blog/exercise-spotlight-snatch]]></link><comments><![CDATA[https://www.strengthcoachglasgow.co.uk/blog/exercise-spotlight-snatch#comments]]></comments><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2020 07:00